products.title: Elsmere Upholstered Sleeper Sofa
products.description: A sleeker sleeper. Just remove the back cushions to turn this asymmetrical sofa into a twin bed – it’s as easy as saying, “You can stay at my place.” Leather accents + strapping elevate durable performance upholstery in an understated hue, and the bolster pillow/armrest can be secured at either end.

products.title: Square Arm Sofa Bed
products.description: Sofa by day, peacekeeper by night. This warm and inviting sleeper flips forward to become a queen-sized sleeper at a moment's notice. Walnut legs coordinate thoughtfully with your choice of fabric.

products.title: Sleeper Sofa
products.description: It's a modern sofa bed that doesn't look like one. Sort of like a wolf in sheep's clothing. Just remove the back cushions and flip the seat forward. Voilà, instant queen-sized mattress. Brushed stainless steel leg.

products.title: Calyna Upholstered Sofa
products.description: Embrace a luxe respite with our elegant and charming Calyna sofa. The plush contours of our sofa are beautifully highlighted with an allover channeling to bring sophisticated style to your home. Featuring a sheltering back and arms with a generously padded seat, our modern sofa delivers sink-in comfort. It is upholstered in the rich and sumptuous textures of boucle in a graceful light grey hue to complement your formal living space and family rooms alike. A true stunner, our sofa offers a cozy nook perfect for both relaxing and entertaining.

products.title: Deans Upholstered Sofa
products.description: This sofa blends smooth curves with plush boucle to create an organic silhouette that’s alluring from every angle. A slightly recessed base gives it a floating quality that completes the cloud-like look. With a solid wood frame and durable upholstery, it’s ready for daily use.

products.title: Sumo Upholstered Loveseat
products.description: As soon as you see it, there can't be any doubt: it's a Fatboy sofa. The Sumo sofa series is soft, strong, tough, and stylish. Overly generous too, immediately making its design iconic. The Sumo sofa was inspired by a collection of cushions but put together cleverly. This modular lounge sofa will transform your living room into your favorite hangout.

products.title: Kearney Upholstered Loveseat
products.description: Round out your space. With its flowing lines and floating seat, this loveseat has a soft + unexpected silhouette that draws on mid-century modern styles. It’s built with a solid wood frame and wrapped in plush, durable velvet, so it’s ready for everyday lounging.

products.title: Ralph Console Table
products.description: This console table showcases a minimalist silhouette with tiered, asymmetrical shelving that becomes a design element in its own right. It’s built from stainless steel with a neutral metallic finish, and its open design offers plenty of storage + display space while keeping sightlines open.

products.title: Dakota Console Table
products.description: Classic design, updated construction. Crafted from solid acacia wood with an iron frame and gold foot caps, this console table’s pared-down lines gives it an airy look. The open, backless silhouette means that each shelf is both storage and display space, so go ahead, show off those plants.

products.title: Carson Console Table
products.description: Sturdy + sleek. With its minimalist lines and high-gloss white finish, this versatile console table won’t add visual clutter to your space. It holds drinks + decor behind the sofa or everyday essentials in the entryway – and even doubles as a small workspace. A single drawer holds keys or coasters.

products.title: Carlo Console Table
products.description: Organic + dynamic. Juxtaposing rustic wood grains against the geometric lines of an inlaid chevron motif, this two-tiered console table is a modern take on farmhouse-inspired style. The bold proportions and black finish of its angular legs add striking edge to a straightforward silhouette.

products.title: Aramis Console Table
products.description: Mixing cool white marble with warm acacia wood grains, this console table’s simple lines keep the focus on contrast + natural texture. It stands on square metal sled legs in a sleek black finish. The broad, asymmetrically divided tabletop offers opportunities for creative styling.

products.title: Kenmore Console Table
products.description: This console table anchors your space with a blend of industrial and rustic styles thanks to its clean-lined silhouette and mixed materials. It's founded atop two curved, black iron supports and a stretcher bar connecting them both.

products.title: Annora Geometric Bookcase
products.description: With a low-profile silhouette and open design, this pared-down bookshelf delivers both storage and sleek minimalism. Crafted from engineered wood, this piece features three tiers of shelving with offset vertical supports.

products.title: Stetson Bookcase
products.description: Compartmentalize your collection. With its 12 asymmetrical cubbies, this Scandi-inspired bookcase offers lots of styling + storage options. The open back lets light through – ideal if you use it as a room divider. It stands either horizontally or vertically, supported by an included wall anchor.

products.title: Innes Ladder Bookcase
products.description: Light industrial. With its vertical storage space and open construction, this ladder bookcase is ideal for styling smaller rooms. It’s built from steel + kiln-dried mango wood, with four tiered shelves to display plants, ceramics, and, yes, even books. Wall-mounting hardware is included.

products.title: Eldorado Etagere Bookcase
products.description: Space age storage. This etagere bookcase features boomerang-style supports that draw on dynamic mid-century design. It’s built from kiln-dried solid walnut wood in a deep brown tone that complements the retro look. With an open silhouette, it’s as visually light as it is striking.

products.title: Ascent Drawer File Cabinet
products.description: Juxtaposing clean lines against rustic woodgrains + black iron hardware, this filing cabinet gives contemporary cabin vibes. Built from solid mango wood, it rolls into your workday on four caster wheels. One drawer holds supplies, while the other has hanging file bars to organize your papers.

products.title: Flame Drawer File Cabinet
products.description: This 2-drawer filing cabinet blends industrial materials with a clean-lined, updated silhouette, so it has you covered when it comes to upgrading your storage options. The outer shell is made from concrete with a distressed finish, which contrasts neatly against the walnut veneers on the drawer fronts.

products.title: Kingsdown Drawer File Cabinet
products.description: The filing pedestal with open shelf and 2 drawers (1 for storage and 1 for filing). The frame is black steel with walnut veneer-covered MDF shelving, panels, and drawers. Coordinates with the desk and bookcase.

products.title: Dang Drawer File Cabinet
products.description: The perforated wood door front allows the use of remotes without spoiling the view. Brass details and wood base.

products.title: Rayford Upholstered Bed
products.description: Reliable retro. With its crisp, low lines + flared, tapered legs, this bed frame draws understated inspiration from mid-century modern style. It’s built from solid wood, in a rich finish that highlights its distinctive natural grain, while the padded headboard shows off tidy button tufting.

products.title: Williams Upholstered Bed
products.description: Mid-century, modernized. This bed features a crisp silhouette with tapered feet that grounds your bedroom with nods to retro design. Upholstery on the rails and headboard softens the look, with foam filling for cushioning while you watch TV + read. Skip the box spring – a slat kit's included.

products.title: Florian Bed
products.description: A fresh angle. This low-profile platform bed’s crisp lines, wide side rails, and sharply tapered legs draw on mid-century style. It’s crafted from solid oak with walnut veneers that layer a warm wood tone onto its sleek silhouette. A panel headboard supports you while you read + stream.

products.title: Antigua Solid Wood Bed
products.description: Inspired by Scandinavian design, this bed frame brings an organic look to your space with its streamlined profile + warm wood grains. It’s crafted from solid wood, with tapered rod legs that echo the rounded edges of its panel headboard, and low side rails for a simple, relaxed look.

products.title: Javi Upholstered Bed
products.description: The nap zone. This platform bed frame blends clean lines, natural wood grains, and neutral upholstery to create a simple, restful vibe in your bedroom. A low profile makes your space feel taller and airier, and the padded headboard invites you to lounge a little longer.

products.title: Kaydan Upholstered Bed
products.description: This low-profile bed frame delivers the effortless bohemianism of a mattress on the floor without any of the social censure. It floats on a recessed plinth base, framed by wide sideboards that flow into two sleek bedside tables. A padded headboard + finished back give you lots of placement options.

products.title: Williams Bed
products.description: Mid-century, modernized. This bed’s clean lines and tapered feet nod to retro designs. The low profile is complemented by the high headboard, so it shows off the warm wood and makes your space feel larger + more open. Before you settle in to rest, grab a box spring.

products.title: Glow Upholstered Bed
products.description: Restful retro. With its crisp lines, low profile, and tapered legs, this platform bed frame draws inspiration from mid-century silhouettes. Coordinating cutouts in the headboard + footboard create satisfying coherence, and the headboard’s linen upholstery offers support while you read or stream.

products.title: Hoboken Desk
products.description: Ground your live-work space with a sleek, ultramodern design with this desk. Crafted from a blend of solid wood and metal, it features a clean-lined rectangular desktop on asymmetrical sled legs, with one running to the floor while the other balances on the drawer pedestal.

products.title: Flame Desk
products.description: The vast workspace of the Broome corner desk is finished in a latte walnut veneer, over a distressed HPL concrete structure. Industrial in style, and perfect for any modern office setting home or professional the Broome corner desk epitomizes sleek practicality.

products.title: Dakota Desk
products.description: Classic design, updated construction. This desk is crafted from solid acacia wood with an iron frame and gold foot caps, for a fresh take on retro design. Double drawers on ball bearing glides keep supplies in easy reach. It fits into a corner of any room, so you can WFW (work from wherever).

products.title: Williams Vanity
products.description: Mid-century, modernized. With its flip-top mirror and three storage compartments, this bedroom vanity helps you get ready, then folds away when it’s not in use. Built with dovetail joints, it's designed to last through moves + milestones. Beveled fronts and tapered legs create a retro vibe.

products.title: Walter Desk
products.description: Mid-century simplicity. This writing desk’s metal accents add a layer of polish to its bold lines + natural acacia wood grains. With a thick glass desktop and dynamic flared legs, it offers space to spread out while bringing an open + airy feel to your WFH office – or living room.

products.title: Lilith Desk
products.description: A desk that elevates your live-work space. Crafted from kiln-dried solid acacia wood in a medium brown finish, its live edge top gives this writing desk a natural look. The top is supported by a matte black-finished iron base, shaped like the wings of a butterfly.

products.title: Flame Desk
products.description: With its expansive surface and pared-down, minimalist silhouette, this desk is great for spreading out while you work. It's made with a solid wood surface with a warm wood grain finish that's set on a gray base, giving it a mixed material look.

products.title: Fischer Dining Table
products.description: Mid-century minimalism. This sculptural dining table’s beveled top rests on sharply angular sled legs. It’s built from solid wood in a rich finish that highlights its natural grain variation, adding an organic element. With seating for up to eight, it’s ready for dinner parties + pizza nights.

products.title: Cal Swivel Office Chair
products.description: Small home office? No problem. This task chair is an eye-catching addition to your office no matter the size. The bucket-style seat has a cutout in the back, and two short arms with a slight scroll for some mid-century modern vibes.

products.title: Marinette Office Chair
products.description: Real talk: If you're on the WFH grind, you need a space that's both stylish and supportive. That's where this desk chair comes in. It's made with an engineered wood seat and has a streamlined, armless silhouette with five gold-finished legs. Translation: It's super easy to match with a modern vibe.

products.title: Jewett Office Chair
products.description: This task chair looks great and will help you get it done. So you can be your best boss self. The seat is built on an engineered wood frame and features a full back with a stylish cutout and armrests.

products.title: Escapade Dining Chair
products.description: Inspired by iconic mid-century design, this bright white side chair’s contoured silhouette base bring space-age style to your dining area. The seat swivels retro-futuristically and features an attached cushion for a little softness while you enjoy your food capsules.

products.title: Cali Swivel Office Chair
products.description: This office chair brings all the modern functionality you need in your workspace with a streamlined look we're all about. It's made with an aluminum frame, and has a pedestal base with five legs and included wheels. The base and seat bottom work together with an adjustable height, center tilt, and swivel, so you can easily adjust this chair and move throughout your space. The seat and back are upholstered in foam-filled dark gray polyester fabric, giving you the support you need while you tackle your workday.

products.title: Lincoln 5 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: Light + nourishing. Inspired by mod mid-century design, this set delivers inviting dining space for four in a pared-back package. The table’s tulip-style pedestal base leaves lots of legroom, while the seats feature padded seats + enveloping arched backrests wrapped in retro leatherette.

products.title: 5 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: With its flared legs, soft lines, and wood grain finishes, this dining set infuses your space with organic + inviting Scandi style. The spacious table is an ideal mealtime companion for four contoured chairs with cushioned seats + floating oval backrests. If only deciding what to eat was this easy.

products.title: Arlener 7 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: This set is ideal for both indoors and outdoors and will make your home ready to enjoy with family and friends. Chairs: Designed under a contemporary influence, these chairs are durable, lightweight but also sturdy. This combination is able to give you the best performance under outdoor conditions. Modern design: Neutral color palette and harmonic lines made this dining set the ideal stylish accessory for your patio and garden.

products.title: Louetta 7 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: We love the way this 7-piece dining set blends warm wood tones and airy, angular silhouettes for an identifiably mid-century look. It includes a table and six chairs, all made from a blend of solid and engineered wood. The table has an oval surface set on a pedestal base with four flared legs, and features a sunburst wood grain design for a balanced aesthetic.

products.title: Ebba 5 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: Take the guesswork out of creating a cohesive look in your dining space. With everything you need for a modern vibe, this 5-piece dining set has you covered. The table features a circular surface to maximize elbow room, with an X-shaped pedestal base and starburst wood grain pattern on the surface for nods to retro designs.

products.title: Daxon 3 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: Comfort food. This dining set mixes mid-century design elements, for a look that’s cohesive without being matchy-matchy. Built from powder-coated steel, the table’s tulip-style silhouette leaves plenty of legroom. The two chairs cradle you in curved seats wrapped with cushioned velvet upholstery.

products.title: Schuyler 5 - Piece Dining Set
products.description: A blend of eclectic materials and striking, mid-century silhouettes gives this 5-piece dining set an airy, yet unmistakably retro look. It includes a table and four chairs. The table is made from solid wood, with a white finish on the reverse-beveled rectangular surface that contrasts with the wood grain finish on the legs and sides. The chairs have molded plastic seats that are set on four-legged Eiffel-style bases, letting you play with an iconic look in your dining room.
